metadata.name: Red Rose
metadata.description:
My last name in Dutch means rose and my favorite color to use in my artworks is red, so I couldn't resist creating an artwork featuring a red rose.  
This is an autobiographical artwork in the sense that it represents my first months in the NFT world. In this beautiful rose you will find a bunch of hidden NFT's I have created.

This NFT comes with a non-exclusive commercial use license that can be found here:  
https://foundation.app/@ArjenRoos/nftcl/1
